{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800920/extras/story.png?t=1647374260\" /><br>Medusa was transformed into a gorgon for defiling Athena's temple while serving as a priestess there. Condemned to spend the rest of her life on a distant isle, she is determined to find a soulmate even though most of her visitors wish to chop off her head! Follow Medusa as she embarks on a journey to prove that even a gorgon can be loved.<br><br>Play through a storyline that is both deep and lighthearted.<br><br>Your actions will determine your fate.<br><br>Defy mortals and the gods!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800920/extras/features.png?t=1647374260\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use your gorgon powers to turn things into stone.<br></li><li> Go on quests.<br></li><li> Meet the gods and other strange and interesting characters from greek mythology.<br></li><li> Talk to your hair.</li></ul><br><i>NOTE: Originally, we planned to make this game three chapters long. Due to changing circumstances, we have decided to release the first chapter as a stand alone game. We hope you enjoy what we were able to finish.</i>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1800920?t=1647374260","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800920/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1647374260","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800920/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1647374260","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800920/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1647374260","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800920/extras/story.png?t=1647374